{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 527\u2089 to base 10**\n527\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070\n= 5\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 7\u00d71\n= 405 + 18 + 7\n= 430\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 408\u2089 to base 10**\n408\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070\n= 4\u00d781 + 0\u00d79 + 8\u00d71\n= 324 + 0 + 8\n= 332\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n430\u2081\u2080 \u00d7 332\u2081\u2080 = 142,760\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 142,760\u2081\u2080 to base 9**\n142,760 \u00f7 9 = 15,862 R 2 \u2192 Check: 15,862\u00d79 + 2 = 142,758 + 2 = 142,760 \u2713\n15,862 \u00f7 9 = 1,762 R 4 \u2192 Check: 1,762\u00d79 + 4 = 15,858 + 4 = 15,862 \u2713\n1,762 \u00f7 9 = 195 R 7 \u2192 Check: 195\u00d79 + 7 = 1,755 + 7 = 1,762 \u2713\n195 \u00f7 9 = 21 R 6 \u2192 Check: 21\u00d79 + 6 = 189 + 6 = 195 \u2713\n21 \u00f7 9 = 2 R 3 \u2192 Check: 2\u00d79 + 3 = 18 + 3 = 21 \u2713\n2 \u00f7 9 = 0 R 2 \u2192 Check: 0\u00d79 + 2 = 2 \u2713\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 236742\u2089\n\n**Step 5: Verify**\n236742\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u2075 + 3\u00d79\u2074 + 6\u00d79\u00b3 + 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070\n= 2\u00d759,049 + 3\u00d76,561 + 6\u00d7729 + 7\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 2\u00d71\n= 118,098 + 19,683 + 4,374 + 567 + 36 + 2\n= 142,760\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n236742", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 703}